
1) Download compressed JSON files with all evidence/association objects (https://www.targetvalidation.org/downloads/data)

2) Uncompress the JSON files

3) Split the big JSON files into smaller chunks for more efficient processing, e.g.:

   cd data-raw/evidence/
   split -l 25000 19.02_evidence_data.json target_validation_evidence_chunk_
   cd data-raw/association/
   split -l 25000 19.02_association_data.json target_validation_association_chunk_

4) Transform the raw JSON chunks to a valid JSON format with 
   ../transform_raw_json_chunks_evidence.py
   ../transform_raw_json_chunks_association.py

5) Retrieve main variables from evidence and association objects 
   nohup ./parse_opentargets.R > parse_opentargets_202002.log &

6) egrep '^symbol|known_drug' opentargets_evidence_202002.tsv > opentargets_evidence_drug_202002.tsv
